    "isActive": false
}

###

### B.2 Confirmar que o boulder desapareceu da listagem (só devolve ativos)
GET http://localhost:8080/gyms/1/boulders
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_DO_OWNER_AQUI

###

### B.3 Reativar o Boulder ID 1
PUT http://localhost:8080/boulders/1/status
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_DO_OWNER_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "isActive": true
}

